{"id":3600,"date":"2014-11-12T11:08:41","date_gmt":"2014-11-12T17:08:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/flaunt_survey_for_interviewers_and_interviewees.php"},"modified":"2014-11-12T11:08:41","modified_gmt":"2014-11-12T17:08:41","slug":"flaunt_survey_for_interviewers_and_interviewees","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/flaunt_survey_for_interviewers_and_interviewees.php","title":{"rendered":"Flaunt Survey for Interviewees and Interviewers"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>We need your help.<\/p>\n<p>One of the most useful features of our <em><a href=\"http:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/flaunt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Flaunt<\/a><\/em> book are the survey results that answer common questions about how to submit and present portfolios for employment consideration and we are updating the answers to reflect five years of change.<\/p>\n<p><strong>There are two parallel surveys:<\/strong><br \/>\n1) <a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/1F7lExf0eZUze9FNnftjxbVJQtSDwtvyt9zhJtEEpEX8\/viewform?c=0&#038;w=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">For those who often make and show portfolios<\/a><br \/>\n2) <a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/1DYgSQadpX-LVpihGPG1pwixOHpsprxBgmH5FE0lcn5A\/viewform?c=0&#038;w=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">for those who often review portfolios<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Please select the one that best suits you. The questions are the same, presented to each group based on their role as interviewee or interviewer. It&#8217;s possible to answer both.<\/p>\n<p>We and thousands of job seekers will be grateful for the time you take in answering the survey. It should take less than 2 minutes.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"We need your help. One of the most useful features of our Flaunt book are the survey results that answer common questions about how to submit and presen